title: Eibach Tech-Tip: Intallation Tip for Brake Components
description: Installing your own suspension can be easy with the right tools. We want to offer some visual tools to our users to help them along with the installation process. Here's a quick video demonstrating how to properly install your new Eibach parts without causing damage to your factory components. This info is relevant to all makes, models and suspension kits.
tags: Eibach, how to install, performance suspension, brakes, ;installation
